some tough love.

69
00:03:10,267 --> 00:03:15,100
Racism is huge
here in Wisconsin,

70
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:17,233
and it's worse
than it's ever been.

71
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:19,767
Milwaukee is kind of special.

72
00:03:19,867 --> 00:03:22,667
This is the Selma of the North.

73
00:03:22,767 --> 00:03:23,967
When I go to other places,

74
00:03:24,067 --> 00:03:25,567
people don't even know
that Milwaukee

75
00:03:25,667 --> 00:03:27,267
have Black folks living here.

76
00:03:27,367 --> 00:03:29,067
Say, "There's Black folks
in Milwaukee?"

77
00:03:29,133 --> 00:03:30,467
Yeah!

78
00:03:30,567 --> 00:03:34,133
And they've been oppressed
like crazy. [laughs]

79
00:03:34,233 --> 00:03:37,067
- Not surprisingly, the highest
demographic representation

80
00:03:37,133 --> 00:03:38,300
