number of persons of color

164
00:07:18,167 --> 00:07:19,633
involved in it.

165
00:07:19,733 --> 00:07:22,367
It makes me somewhat
sensitive to,

166
00:07:22,467 --> 00:07:25,800
hopefully, being able
to address the needs

167
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:30,767
of that population in a way
that is fair to everyone.

168
00:07:30,867 --> 00:07:32,667
- Seymour: Former Madison
police chief Noble Wray

169
00:07:32,767 --> 00:07:34,933
