pardon board.

170
00:07:35,067 --> 00:07:37,767
- The politics back then
was tough on crime,

171
00:07:37,867 --> 00:07:41,100
tough on drugs, say no to drugs.

172
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:45,533
It was, you know,
a zero-tolerance approach.

173
00:07:45,633 --> 00:07:48,200
