than Black people.

198
00:08:49,633 --> 00:08:52,067
If you look at every part
of the system,

199
00:08:52,133 --> 00:08:53,900
it doesn't matter
where you look.

200
00:08:54,067 --> 00:08:57,200
You're going to find
these drivers of disparity.

201
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,767
