some differences,

577
00:25:08,133 --> 00:25:09,567
and if we actually
wanna figure out

578
00:25:09,667 --> 00:25:12,167
how to make this a safe place
for everybody to work,

579
00:25:12,267 --> 00:25:14,533
it's a lot of internal
conversation about things like,

580
00:25:14,633 --> 00:25:17,300
"Hey, you can't say convict,

581
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:20,467
you can't say felon,
here's why."

582
00:25:20,567 --> 00:25:22,633
We gotta figure out
how we got here.

583
00:25:22,733 --> 00:25:24,633
I can preach at you
all this stuff

584
00:25:24,733 --> 00:25:26,300
about the lingo
and the language,

585
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:28,533
and why it's ineffective
