586
00:25:28,633 --> 00:25:30,233
but until people
have a basis

587
00:25:30,333 --> 00:25:32,700
or an understanding
of how we ended up here,

588
00:25:34,367 --> 00:25:35,900
it's a moot point.

589
00:25:36,067 --> 00:25:37,900
- And Dr. Gee,
how do we get all Wisconsinites

590
00:25:38,067 --> 00:25:39,767
to get vested on this?

591
00:25:40,867 --> 00:25:42,667
