that everyone

604
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:11,300
has judicial justice
in their lives.

605
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:13,100
And so I try to invest
in the people

606
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,900
who want to be
a part of the change

607
00:26:15,067 --> 00:26:17,100
and hope that,
at some point,

608
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,600
we will have an impact
on Wisconsin,

609
00:26:18,700 --> 00:26:20,333
but I don't go after
the whole state.

610
00:26:20,433 --> 00:26:22,400
I just try to really
work with the people

611
