00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:43,600
including here in Wisconsin.

668
00:28:43,700 --> 00:28:47,067
- Dr. Christy Clark-Pujara:
The laws against
teaching enslaved people to read

669
00:28:47,167 --> 00:28:49,700
actually come into play

