681
00:29:21,933 --> 00:29:24,333
They would have
inferior school buildings,

682
00:29:24,433 --> 00:29:29,200
inferior materials, inferior
books, or notebooks, right?

683
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:30,933
The teachers
were paid less.

684
00:29:31,067 --> 00:29:34,533
And so, it was
an active disinvestment.

685
00:29:34,633 --> 00:29:36,867
My father was
functionally illiterate.

686
00:29:36,967 --> 00:29:38,700
His family was poor,

687
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:42,100
and he was sharecropping cotton
most of his life,

688
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:46,467
and his labor was essential
to his family's survival,

689
00:29:46,567 --> 00:29:50,833
and the school that
he could attend was underfunded.

690
00:29:50,933 --> 00:29:52,467
- Seymour: During the
