who don't look like us,

1246
00:51:16,667 --> 00:51:18,233
we can't fool
ourselves in thinking

1247
00:51:18,333 --> 00:51:19,633
that we're ready
for a global market,

1248
00:51:19,733 --> 00:51:21,867
